prodNameC: 豐技生物素酵素缺乏症篩檢試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.	Biotinidase Calibrators (1U = nmol/min/dL)(10 U、30 U、130 U、180 U、250 U、350 U) (Whatman, no. 903) containing 5 sets of dried blood spots.
2.	Biotinidase controls(1U = nmol/min/dL)，Normal 275 U、Abnormal 50 U)(Whatman, no. 903) containing 5 sets of dried blood spots.
3.	Biotinidase Reconstitution Buffer 1 bottle, 50 mL
4.	Biotinidase Substrate Reagent 10 vials, lyophilized.
5.	Black microplates (uncoated, 96 wells), 10 plates
6.	Barcode labels for the plate, 30 pcs.
7.	Adhesive microplate covers, 10 sheets
8.	Lot specific quality control certificate, 1 pc
applicantName: 豐技生物科技股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中正區紹興北街5號5樓之1
efficacy: 本試劑為半定量新生兒濾紙血片中生物素酵素活性，用於篩檢新生兒生物素酵素缺乏症。
